  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air</p><p>Cut the <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into thin chips</p><p>Add the <strong>chips</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until crisp</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695646131418-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695646131418-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695646131418-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695646131418-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695646131418-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine 1/4 of the <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>(save the rest for later!) in a bowl with the <strong>curry powder</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your <strong>tandoori</strong> <strong>marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695646134999-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695646134999-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695646134999-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695646134999-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1695646134999-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>free range chicken thighs</strong> to the <strong>tandoori marinade </strong>and give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>marinated chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1695646139247-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1695646139247-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
