            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1695646139247-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>marinated chicken </strong>to one side of a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!)</p><p>Put the tray[s] in the oven for 17-18 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!) and starting to char – this is your <strong>tandoori chicken</strong></p>",
