    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once the chicken is nearly cooked, remove the tray[s] from the oven and add the <strong>sliced brioche bun[s]</strong> to the other side of the tray[s]</p><p>Return the tray[s] to the oven for 3-4 min or until the brioche is warmed through and toasted</p>",
      "order": 7,
